data.description: Buyer incentives includes $6,000 for closing cost or interest rate buy down, and 1 year home warranty. Home offers a dream backyard designed for entertaining--inground heated pool and jacuzzi with security fencing. gazebo, basketball court, several patios,  artificial turf, and 2 additional storage units. Enter via the leaded glass door with side lights into formal living and dining room with vaulted ceiling and clerestory windows. Step up to the kitchen with island and plenty of cabinetry and counter space. Step down into family room with fireplace, opening to back patios. Master bedroom is down with a spacious ensuite including double sinks, jetted tub, separate shower and walk-in closet. Powder room and laundry room completes the downstairs. Follow the winding staircase up to the loft which opens to the rear deck with great views of the city. Three ample sized bedrooms with full bath and walk-in closets completes the upstairs.
